      • NamedExecutorService

        public NamedExecutorService​(String sName,
                            String sDescription,
                            Supplier<ExecutorService> supplier)
        Constructs a new NamedExecutorService. This is a simple wrapper around an executor's logical name and a supplier that produces the ExecutorService itself.
        Parameters:
        sName - the logical ExecutorService name
        sDescription - the description of the ExecutorService
        supplier - the Supplier that will produce the ExecutorService
